data.description: Looking for a perfect 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in a great quiet Negaunee neighborhood? This house is huge; room for everyone in your family to have their own space.  So much about this home is newly redone leaving you to just move in and enjoy; new flooring, new kitchen, new bathrooms, new windows, new boiler, newer roof.  Convenience of the 2 car attached garage with new door. Nice private backyard with deck.
